veila (0.4.4-1) UNRELEASED; urgency=medium

  * Add slideshow crossfade transitions with configurable
    transition_duration_ms (opt-in; default 0 for an instant cut).
  * Fix lock wallpaper flash and delay when sway rewrites the slideshow
    include file: skip include-change reloads on the active curtain session
    and keep the wallpaper fixed for the lock; theme and widgets still
    reload live.
  * Prewarm slideshow wallpapers and the static scene cache before spawn
    to reduce lock latency and cache misses.
  * Fix crossfade when the next wallpaper is already cached: the background
    loader still delivers BuffersReady so the transition can animate.
  * Ignore redundant deferred wallpaper updates when the surface already
    shows the correct image.

 -- Stéphane Cottin <stephane.cottin@vixns.com>  Sun, 05 Jul 2026 20:30:00 +0200

